: null, "praise_count": 1145, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4165, "content": "让你花钱弄会员！", "image": null, "praise_count": 585, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 131118}, {"id": 4167, "content": "QQ的隐私容易泄露", "image": null, "praise_count": 184, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 125955}, {"id": 4168, "content": "我还是喜欢用QQ", "image": null, "praise_count": 499, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142505}, {"id": 4169, "content": "Andriod，windows客户端和iOS，Mac客户端在质量上有太大的差距", "image": null, "praise_count": 60, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 121509}, {"id": 4170, "content": "功能复杂又臃肿，炫酷皮肤非主流", "image": null, "praise_count": 1079, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145458}, {"id": 4187, "content": "长大了", "image": null, "praise_count": 168, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 134400}, {"id": 4188, "content": "受不了一群人在发**的说说和日志（例如失恋后的心灵鸡汤，莫名其妙的八卦新闻）", "image": null, "praise_count": 523, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 106872}, {"id": 4190, "content": "明明可以用手机号加通讯录和微信，为什么还要报一串没规律的qq号，不是6位好意思报么", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493}, {"id": 4191, "content": "以前上QQ只是为了随时截图，自从微信客户端也可以截图之后，曾经“最重要的截图工具”QQ就迷失了产品定位", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 43366}, {"id": 4192, "content": "下意识觉得是PC端产物", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145528}, {"id": 4193, "content": "已经变成办公软件", "image": null, "praise_count": 265, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 140625}, {"id": 4194, "content": "这只是一种习惯，无论看还是不看", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145535}, {"id": 4195, "content": "   用微信更提升逼格", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145527}, {"id": 4197, "content": "QQ太开放了", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145547}, {"id": 4255, "content": "基本是工作需要了", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145627}, {"id": 4256, "content": "上边的人对我不那么重要了", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145636}, {"id": 4266, "content": "QQ用的人还是比较多的，但是现在微信还是主流，他们都有优点或缺点，关键是自己用的好就是好的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 33102}, {"id": 4267, "content": "说的好像微信多么高端似的，还不是土鳖成年人的象征，和QQ一半一半吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145703}, {"id": 4268, "content": "因为存在感变低了。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144969}, {"id": 4270, "content": "不过是一个常用软件而已，微信牛逼？是啊是啊朋友圈嘛我懂的，毕竟是个追求高逼格的时代", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145719}]}